{"tid":749073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵又一單炒梯 目擊者：好似行雷咁嚇死我","createTime":"2018-07-19T17:01:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T00:51:00.000Z","uid":87226,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce8a54e7e79376d12b0a0faea6fc00a70852f58","tid":749073,"uid":87226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:01:18.000Z","msg":"港鐵又炒電梯，睇黎又係用左強國配件....<br />\n聽日出街搭港鐵電梯 各位巴絲要小心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/010025_36d6d9af42a9ef2e437ce13b3cdfcd61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F010025_36d6d9af42a9ef2e437ce13b3cdfcd61.png&h=99bb2541&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我啱啱上完扶手電梯，背後突然傳嚟『嘭』一聲巨響，好似行雷咁。一望原來係炒梯，嚇死我喇！」讀者梁小姐今日晚上約7時，於港鐵旺角站月台乘搭扶手電梯前往大堂，惟當其剛步出扶手電梯時，梯級突然爆開，最頂端有一梯級拱起，梯梳四散，露出長方形空隙。梁身後幾名途人亦受到波及，幸沒有受傷。隨後有港鐵職員到場處理事件。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵發言人表示，晚上7時05分，旺角站車務控制中心職員發現大堂B出入口一條扶手梯的燈號亮起，顯示該扶手梯停止運作。職員趕至了解，發現該扶手梯的頂端梯級及梯梳損毀，立即將其圍封，並召承辦商派員到場維修。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180719&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58462897\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180719%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58462897&d=8H9rfcjeeGVJ9mpqJjXQwLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=278a5cee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180719%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58462897&h=f23861ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180719&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58462897</a>"},{"pid":"2aefa8ca8f1ec6aaa0eb524131ba359a1f76d363","tid":749073,"uid":20816,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"又要搵人在巴士插針了"},{"pid":"ad6ff1b17046b8b038efe12c2574e9b3ea0ef256","tid":749073,"uid":32577,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T17:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知幾時香港會有一個好好彩既人